a guild with let's say 80ppl (6monks) on a raid, so you would say all 6 monks go out and pull for the same raid? there are monks who can pull better, much much better than other monks. Why would you send a monk with low pulling experience out to pull, if you have 1 monk with very high pulling experience? Wouldn't it be better (for the raid), to have the monk with low pulling experience on melee only?<br>
